name: #4-Kitty Pixy
description:
#4-Kitty Pixy
Kitty Pixy is a misunderstood Angel in Kitty Verse.  She is an Angel therefore she provides diamonds to all Kitty's who are good deed doers, kind kitty's, essentially all nice kitty's in Kitty Verse.  But, there is this pixel situation; often times Kitty Pixy can't quite gage where she is traveling to.  Often dropping Diamonds into the uni and missing her Kitty marks? This sends Kitty's scrambling around her through the Verse to try and catch these diamonds! She's so sorry and she likes Pink.
